{"tid":93132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：\t老衲請閉咀","createTime":"2017-01-24T07:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T08:19:38.000Z","uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0671cbcf43f15bd20bb1b612ce8fd44204fc3baf","tid":93132,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61c5082e65fcee0f1aeaaa33e28672ff22a9797","tid":93132,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾會員： 48歲了(破產) 話過退出連登<br />\n屌你老母閪依家番黎做過街老鼠呀柒頭？<br />\n你block撚左我又點 其他人睇到我講咩<br />\n就知你條柒頭過街老鼠番黎比人屌老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔好彩啦 死仆街\t48歲了(破產) <br />\n比我見到你之前話要退出唔再番黎<br />\n屌你老母我話過一定會moon撚住狙擊你條山滋狗<br />\n我睇你係連登做過街死老鼠定做食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0534da5a3d0ecba4658acda6d7611f5fd9896eca","tid":93132,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}